OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,FThe next UK government must better
OL,8,Fregulate the financial sector to
OL,9,Fensure it addresses environmental and
OL,10,Fsocial crises facing the country,
OL,11,Fcampaigners have warned.
OL,13,FA manifesto published by ShareAction,
OL,14,Fwhich campaigns for responsible
OL,15,Finvestment, outlined six key policies
OL,16,Ffor making financial institutions
OL,17,Faddress issues such as climate change,
OL,18,Finequality and degradation of nature.
