OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,FThe document, released on Thursday,
OL,8,Fcomes ahead of UK political parties
OL,9,Funveiling their own manifestos for the
OL,10,Fgeneral election expected this year.
OL,12,FIt said the election "provides the
OL,13,Fnext government an opportunity to
OL,14,Fdemonstrate that the UK remains a
OL,15,Fglobal leader in tackling the enormous
OL,16,Fenvironmental and economic challenges
OL,17,Fwe face".
OL,19,F"Too often, the rules that underpin
OL,20,Finvestment activities act as a barrier
OL,21,Fto innovation," the manifesto added.
