OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,F"UK policymakers have the chance to
OL,8,Fdrive action at scale by setting a
OL,9,Fclear direction and high standards,
OL,10,Fpromoting better regulation and
OL,11,Fincreased transparency, and ensuring
OL,12,Fthat companies and financial
OL,13,Finstitutions are not acting contrary
OL,14,Fto the interests of the society in
OL,15,Fwhich they operate."
