OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,FShareAction is calling for the
OL,8,Fincoming government to introduce
OL,9,Fmeasures such as amending fiduciary
OL,10,Fduty law governing pension funds to
OL,11,Fexpand the definition of savers' "best
OL,12,Finterests" to include impacts on
OL,13,Fpeople and planet.
OL,15,FThe charity also said ministers should
OL,16,Fexpand new anti-greenwashing rules for
OL,17,Fretail funds to institutional
OL,18,Finvestors.
