OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,FOther recommended policies include
OL,8,Fintroducing legislation requiring
OL,9,Fcompanies to report on their social
OL,10,Fimpact and their impact on nature,
OL,11,Fmandatory ethnicity pay gap reporting
OL,12,Ffor large employers and a stronger
OL,13,Fmandatory framework for stewardship
OL,14,Fstandards.
OL,16,FShareAction said many of these
OL,17,Frecommended policy interventions build
OL,18,Fon existing policy initiatives and
OL,19,Fwould require little to no government
OL,20,Fexpenditure to implement.
