OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,FFergus Moffat, head of UK policy at
OL,8,FShareAction, said: "The next
OL,9,Fgovernment will be in power at a
OL,10,Fpivotal moment for people and planet,
OL,11,Fdetermining our country's response to
OL,12,Fthe threats of climate change, nature
OL,13,Floss and inequality.
OL,15,F"Smarter regulation is key to ensuring
OL,16,Fthat finance flows away from polluting
OL,17,Ffossil fuels and exploitative working
OL,18,Fconditions and towards resilient zero-
OL,19,Fcarbon sectors and fairer treatment of
OL,20,Fworkers.
