OL,3,CNext government urged to ensure
OL,4,Cfinancial sector better tackles crises
OL,5,Cfacing UK
OL,7,F"To secure a sustainable future for
OL,8,FBritain, the next government must act
OL,9,Fdecisively to set the highest possible
OL,10,Fstandards for companies and the
OL,11,Ffinancial sector and hold them to
OL,12,Faccount for their impact on all of us."
OL,14,FCarla Denyer, Green Party co-leader,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This is welcome recognition
OL,16,Fthat the private sector has an
OL,17,Fimportant role to play in tackling the
OL,18,Fclimate crisis and helping to create a
OL,19,Ffairer, greener country.
